<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>نا عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٢١٣٨ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ ,<span class="c5"> فِي قَوْلِهِ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{وَتَقَلُّبَكَ فِي السَّاجِدِينَ}</span> <span class="c4">[الشعراء: ٢١٩]</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«فِي الْمُصَلِّينَ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٢١٣٩ - قَالَ عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ قَالَ مَعْمَرٌ ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ قَتَادَةُ:</span> وَقَالَ عِكْرِمَةُ: <span class="c2">«قَائِمًا , وَرَاكَعًا , وَسَاجَدًا , وَجَالِسًا»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>